{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0205d1f2c0","title":"在林伯渠报告上加写的一段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a1b5a009a5","index":0,"year":1944,"month":4,"day":14,"articleId":"0205d1f2c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2118ccd77d","type":"paragraph","text":"在林伯渠报告上加写的一段话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"0205d1f2c0"},{"id":"2c84ac69a3","type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年4月14日）县以上参议会中，可以吸收这种政治态度较右但不是坚决反共分子的少数人（用聘请方法），这对于影响外面的地主资本家与安定本地富有阶层，都有作用。对待他们的态度，要团结和斗争并重，责之以大义，晓之以利害，可使其服从大局。应该给以适当的礼貌与尊重，团结他们，并利用其一技之长，但不可任以要职，更不可假以大权。[1]这是毛泽东在林伯乘报告谈到中间分子的右翼处加写的一段话。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"0205d1f2c0"}],"page":{"id":"3bb709b210","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"0205d1f2c0","start":435,"end":435}}}},"__N_SSG":true}